## Compliance Notice

This software is designed to comply with:
- Turkey Personal Data Protection Law (KVKK)
- Turkish Ministry of Health regulations
- Turkish Medical Association ethics guidelines
- European GDPR standards (where applicable)

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with applicable laws and regulations in their jurisdiction.

## Medical Disclaimer

This software is a tool to assist medical professionals and is not intended to:
- Replace professional medical judgment
- Provide medical diagnosis or treatment recommendations
- Be used without proper medical supervision

Healthcare providers using this software remain solely responsible for patient care decisions and must verify all AI-generated content before clinical use.

## Data Privacy

The software processes medical data and audio recordings. Users must:
- Obtain proper patient consent
- Implement appropriate security measures
- Follow local data protection regulations
- Maintain audit trails as required by law

